26
00:01:57.000 --> 00:02:02.000
The Manus Fear includes the idea that the world is biased against men.

27
00:02:02.000 --> 00:02:06.000
According to the social media influences who promote these views,

28
00:02:06.000 --> 00:02:12.000
being a man means being strong, rich and controlling others, especially women.

29
00:02:12.000 --> 00:02:16.000
As a young boy, Will Adolfi was unlike other boys at school,

30
00:02:16.000 --> 00:02:20.000
