31
00:02:20.000 --> 00:02:25.000
Here, he tells BBC Radio for program Women's Hour how it all started.

32
00:02:25.000 --> 00:02:30.000
I didn't quite fit in the box, I was doing ballet, I wanted to be an actor, I wrote poetry.

33
00:02:30.000 --> 00:02:35.000
And I was an easy target. By the time I got to 14 years old, if you look at pictures of me,

34
