you can see, provide, you can see a mask, I see it.

35
00:02:38.000 --> 00:02:42.000
I unknowingly did my best to adhere to what we call the Man Box,

36
00:02:42.000 --> 00:02:48.000
which is a kind of rigid set of ideals and rules that I may feel pressure as a boy to follow

37
00:02:48.000 --> 00:02:50.000
in order to be a quite unquite real man.

38
00:02:50.000 --> 00:02:53.000
The teenagers can be difficult for someone who's different.

39
00:02:53.000 --> 00:02:58.000
Will enjoyed poetry and ballet, and he says this made him an easy target.

40
00:02:58.000 --> 00:03:01.000
Someone who's vulnerable and easily taken advantage of.

41
00:03:01.000 --> 00:03:06.000
Will responded with bravado, a show of bravery to impress other people,

42
00:03:06.000 --> 00:03:09.000
