43
00:03:09.000 --> 00:03:15.000
He felt pressure to present himself as a quote unquote real man.

44
00:03:15.000 --> 00:03:21.000
The phrase, quote unquote, can be used to show your repeating someone else's words,

45
00:03:21.000 --> 00:03:24.000
especially if you don't agree with them.

46
00:03:24.000 --> 00:03:28.000
But behind the bravado, will struggle to get a girlfriend or hold down a job.

47
00:03:28.000 --> 00:03:34.000
Offline, his life seemed to reflect messages he saw in the videos he was watching online,

48
00:03:34.000 --> 00:03:37.000
that his problems were caused by women.

49
00:03:37.000 --> 00:03:41.000
Here's Will again, sharing more with BBC Radio 4's Women's Hour.

50
00:03:41.000 --> 00:03:46.000
When I went online to search for answers, I had an influencer telling me the world hates men,

51
00:03:46.000 --> 00:03:52.000
which really felt true and it kind of distorted my world view where it got painted over this whole brush,

52
00:03:52.000 --> 00:03:59.000
where I started to feel that was really true that everyone hates men, so it's an us versus them.

53
00:03:59.000 --> 00:04:04.000
Will's view of the world became distorted, twisted out of shape and unrealistic.

54
00:04:04.000 --> 00:04:07.000
He started seeing everyone as an enemy.

55
00:04:07.000 --> 00:04:10.000
