56
00:04:10.000 --> 00:04:16.000
An idea meaning to unfairly think everyone has the same bad qualities as a certain person.

57
00:04:16.000 --> 00:04:19.000
Will saw the world as us versus them.

58
00:04:19.000 --> 00:04:23.000
A phrase which is used to show hostility between two opposing groups.

59
00:04:23.000 --> 00:04:27.000
In this case, the men in the Manusphere and everyone else,

60
00:04:27.000 --> 00:04:33.000
especially women, progressives and the mainstream media, who he believed wanted to limit their power.

61
00:04:33.000 --> 00:04:39.000
Luckily for Will, his experiences in the online world of the Manusphere ended.

62
00:04:39.000 --> 00:04:44.000
But not before his mental health had declined to the point of a breakdown.

63
00:04:44.000 --> 00:04:49.000
Now he visits schools around the UK telling his story to young people,

64
00:04:49.000 --> 00:04:53.000
